        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         The 49th level pet is a Warrior pet.<BR>The 53rd level pet is a Rogue pet.<BR>The 56th level pet is a Monk pet.<BR>The 59th level pet is a Warrior pet.</P><P>59th and 49th have the greatest amount of HP of the pets.  </P><P>53rd level Rogue pet under the right circumstances (back attack 100% of the time) will deal the most damage.</P><P>56th Monk pet will deal the most damage under normal circumstances.</P><P>Rogue and Monk pet have minimal HP (I think 1.2-1.5khp).  Rogue pet has sucky AC.  Monk pet has a fair AC.</P><P>59 Spectre pet has more AC, hits for higher max damage and is immune to fear, but in a Monk vs. Spec pet duel, it's almost a wash.</P><P>So, if you are soloing (fear kiting) and don't need your pet to tank for you, use the Rogue pet.  If you are soloing and fighting resistant MOB's, use the 49 pet. </P><P>Monk pet is a great pet, I use him still at 60.  Rogue pet...haven't used him since I got the monk pet.</P><P></P><P><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=95266" target="_blank">Kuotat Smith</a><BR><s>Warlock</s> Witch<BR>Mithaniel Marr<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
